# ================================================================
# NEXUS.ROOT.V3
# PURPOSE:
#   Root dispatcher for NEXUS when operating on AVIS VERSION 3.
#   This file tells the robot:
#       • VERSION 3 is the active AVIS law
#       • NEXUS must load VERSION 3 resources
#       • All compilation logic is deferred to the NEXUS SDK

# ACTIVE AVIS VERSION:
#   VERSION 3

# AVIS VERSION PATH:
#   ./VERSION 3/

# REQUIRED FILES:
#   ./VERSION 3/AVIS.EDU.FILE
#   ./VERSION 3/AVIS.MANIFEST.EDU
#   ./VERSION 3/robot_avis_schema.json

# NEXUS DIRECTIVE:
#   1. Load AVIS.EDU.FILE as the canonical structural law.
#   2. Load AVIS.MANIFEST.EDU for robot learning order.
#   3. Load robot_avis_schema.json for machine schema rules.
#   4. Ignore all legacy AVIS compilers, engines, and VMs.
#   5. Use NEXUS SDK modules for:
#        - Compilation
#        - Execution
#        - Packaging
#        - Schema enforcement
#        - AI training

# TRANSITION NOTE:
#   This file marks the beginning of the NEXUS era.
#   AVIS tools are frozen at VERSION 3.
#   NEXUS will supersede all AVIS robot tools in VERSION 4.

# END OF ROOT FILE
# ================================================================
